This paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper proposes methods to handle time limits in reinforcement learning, which is a problem that arises in many real-world applications. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
